OL,3,CGovernment's Rwanda bill suffers
OL,4,Cdefeats in Lords
OL,6,FRishi Sunak has suffered five defeats
OL,7,Fin the House of Lords over his Rwanda
OL,8,Fbill.
OL,10,FThe government has previously promised
OL,11,Fthe first flights to the country will
OL,12,Fhappen "in the spring".
OL,14,FIts Bill suffered its first defeat in
OL,15,Fthe House of Lords, as peers backed an
OL,16,Famendment which calls for the
OL,17,Flegislation to comply with domestic
OL,18,Fand international law.
